<p>‚Äú<em>Math is not something boys are better at, it‚Äôs not a spectator sport,
  it‚Äôs not a system of arbitrary rules, it‚Äôs not dependent on the laws of physics,
   it‚Äôs not easier or better in base 12 or base œÄ, it‚Äôs not a young man‚Äôs game,
   it‚Äôs not useless in the real world, it‚Äôs not beholden to the real world, it‚Äôs
    not learnable in one year or from one book or one website, it is not particularly
